🟢 Title:

Customer Support Knowledge Base

🔹 1. Refund Policy

Customers can request a refund within 7 days of delivery.
Refunds are applicable only if:

The product is damaged
The product is defective
The wrong item was delivered

The product must be:

Unused
In original packaging

Refunds are processed within 5–7 business days after approval.

🔹 2. Cancellation Policy
Orders can be cancelled before shipping without any charges
Once the order is shipped, cancellation is not allowed
Customers may refuse delivery, but refund rules will apply
🔹 3. Shipping Information
Standard delivery time: 3–5 business days
Express delivery available with extra charges
Delays may occur due to:
Weather conditions
Logistics issues
🔹 4. Account & Login Issues
Users can reset passwords using “Forgot Password”
Multiple failed login attempts may lock the account temporarily
For account recovery, users must contact support
🔹 5. Payment Information

We accept:

Credit Card
Debit Card
UPI
Net Banking

If payment fails:

Amount is auto-refunded within 3–5 days
Users should avoid multiple rapid retries
🔹 6. Fraud & Legal Issues ⚠️ (VERY IMPORTANT)
Fraud-related complaints must be handled by human support agents
Legal disputes require manual intervention
The system must NOT generate automated responses for such queries
🔹 7. Order Tracking
Users can track orders using Order ID
Tracking updates are available in the account dashboard
🔹 8. General Support Guidelines
The assistant must answer only from available knowledge
If no relevant information is found → escalate to human
Responses should be:
Clear
Polite
Professional